  "body": "Hey React Team!\nI was playing around with transition groups and found that adding a call to requestAnimationFrame seems to help a lot with webkit transitionEnd events firing more consistently. I added a basic catch for browsers without the api call but this is a band-aid solution targeted at recent versions of evergreen browsers. [This chromium bug thread](https://code.google.com/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=388082) helped me a ton in diagnosing the issue on Chrome.\n",
